  "Say": {
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "You don't know this, but Maple World's energy flows strongest in Mu Lung. You could say Mu Lung is the piece that holds the whole puzzle together. When evil is afoot in Mu Lung, you can be sure that Maple World's energy is the goal."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "The people you speak of are after Mu Lung's energy, no doubt. If they were near the Peach Farm, they will soon be upon the forest, where the energy flows strongest. You must follow them."
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirType": "sub"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirType": "string",
          "_value": "There's a forest deep within the farm; a forest teeming with monsters warped by Mu Lung's energy. The Sage Cats are particularly nasty, but I would like you to hunt them."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirType": "string",
          "_value": "Success rarely follows apathy."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "Did you find what you were looking for?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirType": "string",
          "_value": "So they planned to use Mu Lung's energy to control the monsters. But why?"
        }
      },
      "stop": {
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "default": {
          "_dirType": "sub",
          "0": {
            "_dirType": "string",
            "_value": "Two hundred Sage Cats. It will take that many to reveal the full truth, I am sure of it. Find them in the Virtuous Forest near the Peach Farm."
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
